Installation
==================
Need to install cmake(>=3.10), libx11-dev, libxrandr-dev packages
On Ubuntu, these can be install by command:
sudo apt install cmake libx11-dev libxrandr-dev

the source root dir: $MWTM-SRC

build:
    cd $MWTM-SRC
    mkdir build; cd build;
    cmake ..
    make

Cheers :)
